e to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><center>
<p style="text-align:center;"><object width="425" height="344"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/M0khXQImltc&#038;hl=en&#038;fs=1"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/M0khXQImltc&#038;hl=en&#038;fs=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowfullscreen="true" width="425" height="344"></embed></object></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M0khXQImltc">Easy Diabetes Recipes</a></p>
<p></center>
<p>If you have diabetes, you do not have to let it take over your life.  In truth, you can change it into something good by opting to live a healthier way of life.  Having diabetes means that you must eat more veg, drink more water, and exercise some more.  Of course, such things can improve your overall life as a entire. </p>
<p> If you have ever visited a dietician or nutritionist, you were doubtless given information about balanced diets.  You could have even been given a diet plan.  Remember that studies are being conducted on dieting and food all the time, so you want to stay recent with all the latest recipes.  You need to also keep a food diary so that you can keep an eye on every single thing that you eat.  Agree with it or not, you could be eating things that you fully forget.  When writing everything down, you will ensure that you never forget anything that you eat or drink. </p>
<p> There are many amazing easy straightforward Diabetes Recipes available online.  You'll find recipes on thousands of main courses, entre's, snacks, shakes, plant dishes, desserts, etc .  No matter what type of food you like, you'll be able to find easy simple Diabetes Recipes online that are both healthy and delectable. </p>
<p> you may find info concerning the amount of calories in varied recipes.  Such details will help you make a total diet plan.  If you want assistance with making one, you can acquire it from some beneficial internet sites.  You should also visit your doctor and food consultant for help creating a diet plan. </p>
<p> simple straightforward Diabetes Recipes<br /> Shrimp salad :<br /> lb deveined shrimp ( shelled ), but in 2 in. pieces and cooked chilled<br /> one tablespoon minced green onion<br /> 3 tablespoon salad dressing ( your choice, just so long as it is diet )<br /> 3 tablespoon of French dressing ( diet )<br /> cup of cut almonds<br /> cup of fat-free cottage cheese<br /> 2 cup of shredded lettuce<br /> 1 tom.  Cut in wedges<br /> 1 teaspoon of cut parsley sprigs</p>
<p> Mix the 1st six ingredients together. <br /> Divide the lettuce uniformly with parsley and tomato</p>
<p> And that's it!  The calories overall should be around 280. </p>
<p> Ham &amp; cheese roll appetizer :</p>
<p> eight oz of grated Yank cheese<br /> 8 oz of cream cheese<br /> tiny amount of garlic powder<br /> tiny quantity of hot sauce<br /> one tablespoon of Dr Pepper<br /> 2 little packages of shaved ham slices<br /> cup of thinly sliced nuts</p>
<p> Overlap the ham slices as you lay them down. <br /> Mix the other ingredients and blend them together. <br /> Place it over the ham. <br /> Roll the ham slices up to make logs. <br /> make sure that all the cheese is covered. <br /> Keep frozen until time to serve. <br /> Cut into thin slices, and then serve them with crackers! </p>
<p> Strawberries &amp; Cream sugar substitute :</p>
<p> 1 quart of fresh strawberries<br /> ten packets of Splenda sugar SUBSTITUTE ( or 2 tablespoons )<br /> 1 teaspoon of pure vanilla extract<br /> Mint leaves<br /> Light whipped cream</p>
<p> Remove leaves from strawberries. <br /> Wash strawberries and cut them into thin slices. <br /> Place into bowl with sugar substitute and pure vanilla extract. <br /> Mix it all together. <br /> Cover and refrigerate overnight. <br /> Serve in bowls with the whipped topping and garnish with the mint leaves! <br /> Hopefully, you'll enjoy these simple simple Diabetes Recipes!  They should give you an idea about all of the recipes you'll find on the internet.</p>
