      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>So your doctor has just told you that you have diabetes and that you need to get <a href="http://www.adviceondiabetes.com/category/diabetes/diabetic-food/">a diabetic diet</a>sheet and start watching very carefully what you are eating. This is the most complicated among all the issues related to diabetes.</p>
<p>You probably enjoy the foods that you are eating now, and do not have to worry about keeping track of every single thing that you are eating. Now you have to stick to a type 2 diabetes diet plan if this is what your doctor advised you to do, and only do you need to be sticking to a type 2 diabetes diet plan but as well keeping track of when and what you are eating.</p>
<p>The point of this is to be able to provide your doctor, as well as yourself, with the information of what you are eating for your type 2 diabetes diet, and what sort of effect these foods are having on you and your condition.</p>
<p>Good Type 2 Diabetes Diet</p>
<p>So for your type 2 diabetes diet plan, the first thing that you need to learn about is what the good foods are, the foods that you should be including on your diet plan here. There are lots of delicious, <a href="http://diabetesadviceweb.com/category/diabetes/diabetic-food/">healthy foods</a> that you can enjoy on this diet, such as fresh fruits and vegetables, and lots of them.</p>
<p>Whole grain breads and cereals are also going to be very important for you here, so make sure that you are getting two to three servings a day.</p>
<p>Bad Type 2 Diabetes Diet</p>
<p>As well for your type 2 diabetes diet, you need to make sure that you are well aware of the foods that you should not be eating. Anything that is very salty, sugary, or anything processed, is going to be unhealthy for you and should be avoided. It can definitely be hard to stop eating your favorite foods, but once you realize how bad they are for you and how dangerous they are now that you have this condition, you should understand why they should be avoided.</p>
<p>This is all important information for anyone who is <a href="http://diabetespark.com/risks-and-complications-of-a-diabetic/">suffering from diabetes</a>, and who is trying to do good and take care of themselves as best they can. If you don’t do this you are likely to get sick and possibly even die.</p>
<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.diabetescarenow.com">Diabetes Care</a> site, where you can get information and resources about diabetes symptoms, gestational diabetes, and more.<br/><br/><a href="http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/following-type-2-diabetes-diet-plan/">Following Type 2 Diabetes Diet Plan</a></p>


