      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>If you have diabetes then you are going to need to learn more about your condition and learn about the different things that you can do to manage it and make sure that you are always in the best health. It is really important that you follow a pre diabetes diet or something of the sort, and this way your condition is not going to get out of control and possibly even be life threatening.</p>
<p>How to Get Started With Type 2 Diabetes Diet</p>
<p>If you want to get started with a <a href="http://adviceondiabetes.com/">type 2 diabetes diet plan</a> then you are going to need to first learn about insulin resistance. This is the only way that you are going to be able to figure out what type 2 diabetes diet is going to be right for you and how to learn about the different things that you are going to need to be eating.</p>
<p>So before you create your own type 2 diabetes diet plan, there are some things that you are going to want to be aware of.</p>
<p>For one you need to realize that the majority of people with <a href="http://adviceondiabetes.com/diabetes-care/diabetes-management-in-primary-care-settings-is-where-diabetes-management-begins/">type 2 diabetes</a> are insulin resistant which means that the insulin that is produced does not work very efficiently and there are large amounts are needed in order to keep the blood glucose levels down. This means you should not only take eat proper food but be busy in your daily life.</p>
<p>You can control your condition by doing proper exercise.</p>
<p>Now for your <a href="http://adviceondiabetes.com/diabetes/diabetic-food/get-the-best-choices-for-fast-food-for-diabetics/">type 2 diabetes diet</a> you are going to need to make sure that you eat lots of legumes. These are enriched with plenty of proteins hence you should use them in your diet minimum one time daily. You also need to be eating lots of fresh fruit but you should try to eat the majority of them in the morning so that your body can work off the natural sugars before the end of the day.</p>
<p>These are all important things that you want to be aware of when it comes to creating a diet plan for your diabetes condition. You are going to need to work with your doctor and hopefully a nutritionist as well so that you can come up with the best diet plan for you.</p>
