tes_Test_Tips.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><center>
<p style="text-align:center;"><object width="425" height="344"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/54fFsticxV4&#038;hl=en&#038;fs=1"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/54fFsticxV4&#038;hl=en&#038;fs=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowfullscreen="true" width="425" height="344"></embed></object></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=54fFsticxV4">Diabetes Test</a></p>
<p></center>
<p>To find out if you're a diabetic the neatest thing that you can do is to contact your physician and have them to plan a glucose tolerance test.  This test is preformed over a period of a couple of hours and will help to judge how your body is reacting to sugar.  At the end of the test, the results will permit your doctor to establish whether to diagnose you as a diabetic or not. </p>
<p> if you are female and you've ever been pregnant then you already know what this test is.  To some people it isn't enjoyable due to the flavor of the liquid that you've got to drink ; although others find that it tastes just like a very sweet soda or cool-aid. </p>
<p> The Test - Your consultant will indoctrinate you not to drink or eat after midnight the night before you are scheduled to have this test preformed ; hence you may probably need to make sure that your test is lined up for early in the morning.  You've got to fast before the test or the results will not be correct, so don't lie to the surgeon and attempt to sneak in something to eat or drink that morning.  You need to have a correct account of how your body reacts to sugar intake if you're the least little bit worried whether you are a diabetic or not. </p>
<p> You'll be given a specific amount of extraordinarily sweet liquid to drink.  Today, there are different flavors that are available for you to select from and it can help to make your experience slightly better if the facility offers the different selections.  Flavours like orange, grape and fruit punch are sometimes very hot.  You have to drink this liquid inside a certain time frame, that the medical care pro who administers the test will inform you of.  When you have finished the test, you will then be timed and after certain time duration, they will draw blood. </p>
<p> Yyou may then need to wait another hour and then they are going to draw blood again.  Usually, this test last 3 hours and they will draw blood roughly three times across the test.  After you are done with the test, you'll then be able to eat or drink normal foods.  Once the results come back, your surgeon will be informed and relying on the results, you'll either be diagnosed as a diabetic, a pre diabetic, a non diabetic or most likely even asked to take the test again. </p>
<p> The diabetes test may seem like a headache because of the period of time that's needed on your behalf ; however, it's a very good idea that you have this test done if you think that you could be showing some signs or evidence of a diabetic.  It is in your best interest to follow through with this test. </p>
<p> There are another ways a physician can determine whether you are a diabetic or not, but this is the most typical test that is preformed in today's medical facilities. <br /> .</p>
