      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>If you or a relations member has been diagnosed with diabetes Type 2, you maybe have lots of questions. First of all, what's the cause of <a href="http://best-health-beauty.us/diabetes-type-2">diabetes Type 2</a>?</p>
<p> Diabetes Type 2 is the insulin-reliant form of the disorder. The pancreas, like several other parts of the body, works less healthy as it gets adult.</p>
<p> In this form of diabetes mellitus, the pancreas somehow does not create enough insulin. There is evidence that insulin-independent diabetes is genetic. If a relations member is diabetic, there is a strong chance you will also develop the disorder as you age. Most often, however, the cause of diabetes Type II is overweight. If you devour too much, your pancreas cannot create enough insulin to successfully handle the glucose you consume in your food.</p>
<p> Therefore, the most excellent plan to remedy your diabetes is to eat properly. Your doctor or dietician will recommend a diet to specially meet your requests. In general, this diet will range from 800 to 1500 <a href="http://best-health-beauty.us/hair-thinning">calories</a> per day, depending on your weight and height.</p>
<p> In addition to following the diet, you should also devour small portions of carbohydrates at scheduled intervals each day. You should also avoid sweets and alcohol. Whole grain breads as well as vegetables are recommended.<br /> If you do not follow it, you may increase troubles with your eyes, nerves, kidneys and feet. Some people have had to find their toes, feet or legs amputated because of poor diabetic control. There is increased risk of heart attack or stroke.</p>
<p> Unlike insulin-dependent (or Type 1) diabetes, diabetes type 2 is relatively simple to control. Often the condition resolves itself once the patient loses enough weight.</p>
<p> No matter the cause of diabetes type II, you be able to lead a full and normal life if you acquire care to follow your treatment plan. With today's importance on healthy intake, this is <a href="http://best-health-beauty.us/cheap-health-insurance">easier than ever</a>.</p>
