      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><center>
<p style="text-align:center;"><object width="425" height="344"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/D03aMGsr7Rc&#038;hl=en&#038;fs=1"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/D03aMGsr7Rc&#038;hl=en&#038;fs=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowfullscreen="true" width="425" height="344"></embed></object></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D03aMGsr7Rc">American Diabetes Association</a></p>
<p></center>
<p>The Yankee Diabetes organisation is devoted to help fight, and find a cure for diabetes.  Diabetes is a threatening car immune illness.  For some reason the body attacks itself and destroys certain cells in the pancreas that help to provide insulin ; although we don't know why the body destroys these cells.  Until we will figure this out, there will not be a treatment cure} for diabetes. </p>
<p> A Great Organization - The Yank Diabetes association is the leader in raising cash for the cure, organizing events and helps to pay for the despairingly needed research to help stop, cure or manage diabetes.  They publish the findings that are a consequence of the in depth research and this keeps medical professionals, the general public and those suffering from from diabetes informed.  They're employed with the families and with those who are diagnosed as a diabetic to help educate them so they are better able to maintain and control their blood glucose levels and live ordinary, healthy lives.  They also act as an advocate to ensure that people who have diabetes are ensured rights and aren't unfairly treated. </p>
<p> The American Diabetes organisation can help to provide a wide variety of information on and about all forms of diabetes and fundamentally anything that relates to the illness.  They can help you learn about pre diabetes, Type one or Type two and gestational diabetes.  If you would like to contact them to receive information about diabetes or events that are planned that will help to raise money for the cure, call 1-800-Diabetes or visit www.diabetes.org. </p>
<p> There are approximately twenty-four million kids and adults in the united states who have diabetes.  The Yankee Diabetes association is their advocate and you can help.  You can contact the organization to learn about the different ways in which you can volunteer. </p>
<p> This organization can definitely provide you with any answers that you may have about diabetes, whether or not it is about management and control or prevention.  They can teach you recommendations on how to eat healthy and exercise that will allow you to maintain a healthy way of life.  Whatever the truth might be the American Diabetes association will help you by providing information to you that may help you or permit you to help a loved one to live a productive life in spite of their disease. </p>
<p> They take donations from prepared customers to help fund the analysis and the other services that they supply.  You can take a role in the many Walk for Diabetes that they host across the country if it is a community event or merely a school event.  All help is seriously appreciated and required, not only by the American Diabetes association but also by the twenty-four million youngsters and adults who live with this illness across the U.  S.   every day. </p>
<p> Without the American Diabetes organisation and the efforts that they have made, we wouldn't be where we are at today apropos the medical progress and management methods that have been developed to help fight diabetes.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Come visit us here for your three free Diabetic Diet Ebooks: <a href="http://diabeticdietzone.com/">American Diabetes Association</a> http://diabeticdietzone.com.</p>
