      <title>A Guide to Diabetes Mellitus Causes and Treatment</title>
      <link>http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-mellitus/a-guide-to-diabetes-mellitus-causes-and-treatment/</link>
      <comments>http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-mellitus/a-guide-to-diabetes-mellitus-causes-and-treatment/#comments</comments>
