      <description><![CDATA[Having type 1 diabetes can be scary.  The complications for type 1 diabetics are serious, especially for those who neglect to care for their diabetes.  Those with type 1 diabetes are at risk for the following complications:
 

Getting heart disease (aka cardiovascular disease)
Going blind (aka retinopathy)
Getting nerve damage (aka neuropathy)
Getting kidney damage (nephropathy)

 

One of the most [...]<p>This post via the <a href="http://www.diabetescarenow.com">Diabetes Care</a> site, where you can get information and resources about diabetes symptoms, gestational diabetes, and more.<br/><br/><a href="http://www.diabetescarenow.com/type-1-diabetes/type-1-diabetics/">Type 1 Diabetics</a></p>



More Diabetes Care information:<ol><li><a href='http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/have-courage-you-can-effectively-manage-diabetes-and-live-a-better-life/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Have Courage  You Can Effectively Manage Diabetes and Live A Better Life'>Have Courage  You Can Effectively Manage Diabetes and Live A Better Life</a> <small> When people are first told by their doctors that...</small></li><li><a href='http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/you-can-adjust-your-life-with-diabetes-know-how/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: You Can Adjust Your Life with Diabetes : Know How'>You Can Adjust Your Life with Diabetes : Know How</a> <small> A lot of people with diabetes just can’t seem...</small></li><li><a href='http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/following-type-2-diabetes-diet-plan/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Following Type 2 Diabetes Diet Plan'>Following Type 2 Diabetes Diet Plan</a> <small> So your doctor has just told you that you...</small></li><li><a href='http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/vital-pieces-of-diabetes/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Vital Pieces Of Diabetes'>Vital Pieces Of Diabetes</a> <small> If your body does not produce insulin the right...</small></li><li><a href='http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/important-factors-that-will-help-you-conquer-diabetes/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Important Factors That Will Help You Conquer Diabetes'>Important Factors That Will Help You Conquer Diabetes</a> <small> Diabetes is a disease where cure is yet to...</small></li></ol>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Having type 1 diabetes can be scary.  The complications for type 1 diabetics are serious, especially for those who neglect to care for their diabetes.  Those with type 1 diabetes are at risk for the following complications:</p>
<p> </p>
<ul>
<li>Getting heart disease (aka cardiovascular disease)</li>
<li>Going blind (aka retinopathy)</li>
<li>Getting nerve damage (aka neuropathy)</li>
<li>Getting kidney damage (nephropathy)</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><a title="Syringe" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/22280677@N07/3424767916/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft" style="border: 0px initial initial;" title="Type 1 Diabetics" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3319/3424767916_a9a62be673_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Syringe" width="240" height="180" /></a><br />
One of the most important thing people with diabetes can do is take care of themselves.  "Taking care" means learning about the right type of meals to prepare and eat, eliminating alcohol and tobacco intake, and working with doctors and dietitians to learn about how to care for their eyes, feet, and skin.</p>
<p>If you or a loved one has type 1 diabetes, do not hesitate to contact your family doctor to get more information on how to live a healthy life with diabetes.</p>
