More Diabetes Care information:<ol><li><a href='http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/keep-blood-sugar-levels-normal-by-following-a-gestational-diabetes-diet-plan/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Keep Blood Sugar Levels Normal By Following A Gestational Diabetes Diet Plan'>Keep Blood Sugar Levels Normal By Following A Gestational Diabetes Diet Plan</a> <small> One of the best means by which a person...</small></li><li><a href='http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/learning-gestational-diabetes-recipes/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Learning Gestational Diabetes Recipes'>Learning Gestational Diabetes Recipes</a> <small> Gestational Diabetes Recipes Approximately five percent of all pregnant...</small></li><li><a href='http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/gestational-diabetes-meal-plan-tricks-information/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Gestational Diabetes Meal Plan Tricks Information'>Gestational Diabetes Meal Plan Tricks Information</a> <small> Gestational Diabetes Meal Plan There are three types of...</small></li><li><a href='http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/gestational-diabetes-diet-tips-and-information/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Gestational Diabetes Diet Tips and Information'>Gestational Diabetes Diet Tips and Information</a> <small> Gestational Diabetes Diet Gestational diabetes is just as serious...</small></li><li><a href='http://www.diabetescarenow.com/diabetes-care/tips-and-tricks-to-free-diabetes-recipes/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Tips and Tricks to Free Diabetes Recipes'>Tips and Tricks to Free Diabetes Recipes</a> <small> Free Diabetes Recipes If you have lately conducted an...</small></li></ol>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div style="float:left; padding: 12px"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2009/03/diabetes1.jpg"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2009/03/diabetes1.jpg" alt="" /></a></div>
<p>Whenever a group of people get together and bring food, there is always a chance that someone there may be diabetic.  While most people may not think twice about this, some may wonder, "What are the best foods for diabetics?"</p>
<p>The severity of the diabetes will determine what a diabetic should or should not eat.  If you are worried, then you can offer a variety of options, including:</p>
<ul>
<li>Fruit and veggie tray with dip</li>
<li>Sweets made (or baked) with fruit sugar, instead of refined sugar, as fruit sugar is sweeter so less is used</li>
<li>Sugar-free candies and cookies, made specifically for diabetics</li>
